title: Bindaas
subTitle: Abhi falls in love with Kajol and convinces her family to get them married. However, things get complicated when Kajol's uncle asks him to kill their rival's son, who is none other than Abhi himself.

title: Eagoler Chokh
subTitle: A senior police officer and his assistant investigate a young woman's murder. As the case unfolds, he learns more about human psychology and the intricacies of his own mind.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Tarakasura sends an assassin to kill Mainadevi and plans to frame Lord Shiva. The assassin puts poison in Mainadevi's food.

title: Premer Pratidan
subTitle: Besotted with Radha, Sandip journeys to Shimla to profess his love. Though he eventually wins her heart, their newfound happiness proves fleeting.

title: Mahapith Tarapith
subTitle: Sameer Roy, a lawyer, is a devotee of Tara Maa while his friend, Ajay, does not believe in God. When Ajay's son falls sick, Sameer believes that only Tara Maa can save him.

title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Sathi
subTitle: A singer accidentally causes a woman to lose her sight. Driven by guilt, he decides to help her achieve her dreams, while she remains unaware of his identity.

title: Chore Chore Mastuto Bhai
subTitle: John is hired by Nagraj to steal a diamond but ends up betraying him, inviting his ire. Before Nagraj's henchman kills John, he gives the diamond to a taxi driver for safekeeping.

title: Challenge
subTitle: Pooja, the daughter of a ruthless businessman who cannot tolerate any male advances towards her, falls for Abir. However, when her father learns about their relationship, all hell breaks loose.

title: Badla
subTitle: Bharti Devi leads a happy life with her three sons, Jay, Sujay and Arjun. However, Sanatan decides to break their family apart in order to settle past scores with Bharti, who he believes wronged him.

title: Badla

title: Krishna Bhakta Sudama
subTitle: Krishna's close friend, Sudama, goes through a chronicle of challenges and hardships.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainadevi holds Lord Shiva responsible for the danger that happened. The devas become shocked when Lord Shiva asks Lord Vishnu to marry Parvati.

title: Mon Chaye Tomay
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Mayer Dibbi
subTitle: Digambar, a businessman, attempts to destroy his rival, Mahendra Pratap Chowdhary. However, things take a turn when Mahendra's son hinders his plans.

title: Santan Jakhan Satru
subTitle: Shubhendu, a devoted father, is betrayed by his two sons when he experiences heavy losses in his business. Fortunately, his adopted son comes to his aid.

title: Bidhilipi
subTitle: A schoolmaster's former student, Bablu, falls in love with his daughter, Minu. However, Minu is in love with another man, Alok, and wants to marry him.

title: Ami Sudhu Cheyechhi Tomay
subTitle: Rich but lonely and well-intentioned Abhi comes across his childhood love, Bhoomika, when both enrol in the same college. Despite many challenges, he resolves to win her love and friendship.

title: Premi
subTitle: Sumit, a football player, loses his leg while trying to save Rahul, his best friend. Fate plays a cruel joke when the girl Rahul loves is about to be married off to Sumit.

title: Mahakaal
subTitle: Prof. Ajoy Mukherjee and his wife testify against criminal Digbijay, leading to unforeseen consequences. Their son Joy becomes entangled in a dangerous web of deceit.

title: Mahakaal
subTitle: Prof. Ajoy Mukherjee and his wife testify against criminal Digbijay, leading to unforeseen consequences. Their son Joy becomes entangled in a dangerous web of deceit.

title: Bornoporichoy
subTitle: Dhananjoy, a police detective, goes on a desperate lookout for Arko, a man who murders people, taking inspiration from the five elements- Earth, Water, Wind, Sky, and Fire.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainadevi approaches Narayan and requests him to marry Parvati, and he accepts her proposal. Narayan impersonates Lord Shiva to meet Parvati.

title: Fight 1:1
subTitle: Two rival groups compete against each other in all aspects of their college life. However, the only obstruction to their growing enmity is their extremely disciplined dean.

title: Nayaner Alo
subTitle: A village singer moves to the city to follow his dreams, where he meets supportive allies who help him navigate fame, ambition and emotional upheaval in an unfamiliar world.

title: Maan Maryada
subTitle: Yogesh, a selfless man, takes care and raises his two step-brothers, a step-sister and an orphan boy. However, when things go south and he becomes bankrupt, his step-siblings abandon him.

title: Sejo Bou
subTitle: A poor man falls in love with a girl belonging to a wealthy family. In an attempt to separate them, the man is sent abroad. However, the couple's destiny intervenes, striving to bring them together.

title: Hullor
subTitle: Two married couples try to save a grocery store from greedy realtors who wish to develop a mall in its place. However, they must overcome several challenges in their quest.

title: Sasur Bari Zindabad
subTitle: While running away from an arranged marriage, Rupa meets Sonu, a mechanic who changes her life forever.

title: Khiladi
subTitle: Two families of opposing faiths are in a long-standing rivalry over land and past wounds. However, one man vows to reunite them by disguising himself as a Hindu person.
